Label: LABEL
Description: A rdfs:comment

Label: has package type
Description: Indicates the package type of a Package Statement

Label: has package type medical subtype
Description: Indicates the package subtype in case the intervention is medication

Label: has status
Description: Indicates the editorial status of the Package Statement

Label: has assessment type
Description: Indicates the assessment type of a Package Statement

Label: has indication
Description: The indication that an IIC assessment is about

Label: has intervention
Description: The intervention that a IIC assessment is about

Label: has IIC assessment
Description: An IIC assessment that a Package Statement covers

Label: has EMSMP
Description: The discussion of EMSMP for an IIC
Range: Established Medical Science and Medical Practice

Label: has PICO
Description: The PICO that is defined for an EMSMP investigation
Domain: Established Medical Science and Medical Practice

Label: has systematic literature review
Description: The search for evidence and results for the EMSMP evaluation
Domain: Established Medical Science and Medical Practice

Label: has date limit
Description: The date limit for a search for evidence

Label: has evidence type
Description: The type of evidence (RTC, Systematic review etc) that was searched for

Label: has outcome measurement
Description: The actual value of a outcome measure that is part of the EMSMP evaluation
Domain: Established Medical Science and Medical Practice

Label: has BIA
Description: The Budget Impact Analysis for an IIC

Label: has scenario
Description: The scenario for a BIA dataset

Label: has trend assumption
Description: The trend assumption dataset of a BIA

Label: has cost estimation
Description: The cost estimation dataset of a BIA

Label: has cost type
Description: The cost type dimension of a particular cost estimation value

Label: has conclusion
Description: The conclusion about a ICC assessment, expressed as positive or negative

Label: has relative effectiveness
Description: The relative effectiveness of a Intervention for an Indication, expressed as positive, negative, or equal
Domain: Established Medical Science and Medical Practice

Label: has cost-effectiveness
Description: The discussion of cost-effectiveness for an IIC

Label: has managed entry agreement
Description: A managed entry agreement for a IIC
